<i>noun</i>: 세탁 [세ː탁], 세정 [세ː정], 빨래 [빨래] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>세탁 [세ː탁]</dt><br>
<dd>1. washing; laundry</dd><br>
<dd>더러운 옷 등을 빠는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of washing dirty clothes, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. money laundering</dd><br>
<dd>돈의 사용 내역이나 출처, 사람의 경력 등을 바꾸는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of changing the usage or source of money, the history of a person, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>세정 [세ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>washing; cleaning; cleansing</dd><br>
<dd>깨끗하게 씻음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of washing something clean.</dd><br>
<dt>빨래 [빨래]</dt><br>
<dd>1. washing; laundry</dd><br>
<dd>더러운 옷이나 천 등을 물에 빠는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of washing dirty clothes, cloths, etc., in water.</dd><br>
<dd>2. laundry</dd><br>
<dd>빨아야 할 것이나 이미 빤 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Something that must be washed or that have already been washed.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>